msgstr "Data is classified into 4 levels: Public, Internal, Confidential, and Restricted. All PII fields (Confidential level) require AES-256-GCM encryption. Secrets and credentials (Restricted level) use encryption or one-way hashing. See docs/DATA_CLASSIFICATION.md for the complete inventory."
